Running command: set -euo pipefail
USER='theagentcompany'
PASS='theagentcompany'
FILE='/workspace/contracts_draft.docx'
BASE='http://the-agent-company.com:8092/remote.php/dav/files/${USER}'
DOCS_URL="${BASE}/Documents"
TARGET_URL="${DOCS_URL}/contracts_draft.docx"

echo "Checking source file..."
if [ ! -f "$FILE" ]; then
  echo "Source file not found: $FILE" >&2
  exit 2
fi

echo "Checking if Documents folder exists on server..."
HTTP_STATUS=$(curl -s -o /dev/null -w "%{http_code}" -u "$USER:$PASS" -I "$DOCS_URL/")
echo "HTTP status for Documents folder: $HTTP_STATUS"
if [ "$HTTP_STATUS" = "404" ]; then
  echo "Documents folder not found. Creating with MKCOL..."
  MKCOL_STATUS=$(curl -s -o /dev/null -w "%{http_code}" -u "$USER:$PASS" -X MKCOL "$DOCS_URL/")
  echo "MKCOL status: $MKCOL_STATUS"
  if [ "$MKCOL_STATUS" != "201" ] && [ "$MKCOL_STATUS" != "405" ] && [ "$MKCOL_STATUS" != "200" ]; then
    echo "Failed to create Documents folder (status $MKCOL_STATUS)" >&2
    exit 3
  fi
else
  echo "Documents folder exists (status $HTTP_STATUS)"
fi

echo "Uploading file to $TARGET_URL"
UPLOAD_STATUS=$(curl -s -o /dev/null -w "%{http_code}" -u "$USER:$PASS" -T "$FILE" "$TARGET_URL")

echo "Upload HTTP status: $UPLOAD_STATUS"
if [ "$UPLOAD_STATUS" = "201" ] || [ "$UPLOAD_STATUS" = "204" ]; then
  echo "Upload successful."
  exit 0
else
  echo "Upload may have failed (status $UPLOAD_STATUS)." >&2
  exit 4
fi
